name: The Trees and The Life #003-Baluran
description:
It was the third time. It had changed a lot, in a good way of course. No more bumpy road, easy access sign. No luck meeting residential deer, buffalo, and the peacock. Sun shining hard, even made the road look oily. Trees full of Long Tail Macaca taking shade from the heat, even the trees shed their leaves to survive.

The Trees and The Life is a 10-Photo-Based-NFT Collection made by Danar Tri Atmojo. As the first-ever collection made, Danar dedicated these NFT's to mother nature as we move towards the new era of digitalization using Tezos blockchain as #CleanNFTs.
